sentences: Julian Dzeko (born May 3, 1992), known mononymously as Dzeko, is a Canadian DJ and record producer.
Known as a former member of the DJ duo Dzeko & Torres, he left the group to pursue a solo career in 2016.
Dzeko released "Liberty" as a single on December 12, 2016, as well as "Never Gonna Love Me" on February 2, 2017 on Armada Deep.
On December 8, 2017, Dzeko was invited by the Harvard College Electronic Music Collective to lecture on the state of the music industry.
In 2018, Dzeko collaborated with Dutch DJ TiÃ«sto alongside featured guests Preme and Post Malone, to release the single "Jackie Chan".
